      • getOwnerUnit

        public Unit getOwnerUnit()
        Returns the unit owning this UnitContainer. If this UnitContainer is an instance of class Ship or Building the normal owning unit is returned (or null, if there is none). In case of a Region, the OwnerUnit of the largest castle is returned. In case of a Faction, null is returned.
        Specified by:

      • hasCache

        public boolean hasCache()
        Description copied from interface: HasCache
        Returns false if this unit does not have a cache. The reverse is not always true:
        If this method returns false, a subsequent call to getCache() will always create a new cache.
        If this method returns true, a subsequent call to getCache() may or may not create a new cache.
        Specified by:
        hasCache in interface HasCache
        See Also:
        HasCache.hasCache()
